HOW TO COMPILE
-----------------------------------------
Mac/Linux:
  gcc -Wall -O2 -o timedexec timedexec.c -lpthread

Windows:
  gcc -Wall -O2 -o timedexec timedexec.c -lpthread
  (run inside WSL terminal, same command)
